cu.explanation_en: Setting the S1U port to an out-of-range value of 99999 will cause port binding failures and prevent GTP-U tunnel establishment.

du.explanation_en: Setting the PRACH configuration index to an invalid value of 200 will exceed the maximum allowed index and cause RACH configuration errors.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PRACH 配置索引設定為無效的值 200，將超過允許的最大索引，並導致 RACH 配置錯誤。
